        </nav>
      </header>

      <section class="fade" style="--d: 1">
        <p>I work on machine learning for drug discovery.</p>
        <p>
          At Genesis Molecular AI, I built the distributed data systems behind
          <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2510.24670">Pearl</a>, a foundation model
          for protein structure, and an active learning platform that screened
          billions of compounds with ML in the loop. My job sat between research
          and production: turning models into systems that ran inside live drug
          programs, often in weeks.
